# thoth_siem_settings

Manages SIEM provider selection and SIEM webhook routing details.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_siem_settings" "siem" {
  siem_provider         = "custom"
  siem_webhook_enabled  = true
  siem_webhook_url      = var.siem_webhook_url
  siem_webhook_secret   = var.siem_webhook_secret
  siem_webhook_provider = "custom"
}
```
